    "code": "012", 
    "data": "As per the traditions of the infallible Imams (a.s.), the day of Friday is reserved for the Imam of the Time, Imame’ Zamana (a.s.). Since Friday is largely considered as the day of zohoor (reappearance) of the Imam, this ziyarat assumes that much more importance. While it is essential for the Shiah to convey salaam to Imam every day, this ziyarat is special because it is recited on the day reserved for the Imam (a.s.). In this ziyarat, the believer salutes the Imam (a.s.) through his forefathers and affectionately calls out to the Imam (a.s.) saying that since this is Friday; the day on which your zohoor is ordained, come soon and extract revenge from the enemies of Allah and your enemies and please the hearts of the believers through that. Then the believer pleads to Imam (a.s.) saying, O my master, on this day, I am your guest. You are an marvellous host, you are generous and the son of generous (Imams). So be an excellent host to me!\nOne of the benefits of reciting these loving sentences is that Inshallah, when the Imam (a.s.) arrives, he will remember our dua and invite us to be his guest. It is the habit of worldly parents that they remember the requests of their children. Imam (a.s.) loves us more than our parents and therefore he will remember our request well. Hence one should not forsake the recitation of this special ziyarat on Friday.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا حُجَّةَ اللهِ فِیْ اَرْضِهٖ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA HUJJATAL LAAHE FEE ARZEHI \nPeace be upon you, O argument of Allah in His lands!\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا عَيْنَ اللهِ فِیْ خَلْقِهٖ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA AYNAL LAAHE FEE KHALQEHI \nPeace be upon you, O sight of Allah on His creatures!\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا نُوْرَ اللهِ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA NOORAL LAAHIL \nPeace be upon you, O light of Allah\nالَّذِیْ يَهْتَدِیْ بِهِ الْمُهْتَدُوْنَ \nLAZEE YAHTADEE BEHIL MOHTADOONA \nby which those who have been guided [to the true guidance] are guided\nوَ يُفَرَّجُ بِهٖ عَنِ الْمُوْمِنِيْنَ \nWA YOFARRAJO BEHI A’NIL MOMENEENA \nand by which the believers are relieved!\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ اَيُّهَا الْمُهَذَّبُ الْخَآئِفُ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA AYYOHAL MOHAZZABUL KHAAA-EFO \nPeace be upon you, O polite and fearful! \nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ اَيُّهَا الْوَلِیُّ النَّاصِحُ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA AYYOHAL WALIYYUN NAASEHO \nPeace be upon you, O sincere patron! \nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا سَفِيْنَةَ النَّجَاةِ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA SAFEENATAN NAJAATE \nPeace be upon you, O ark of salvation!\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا عَيْنَ الْحَيَاةِ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA A’YNAL HAYAATE \nPeace be upon you, O essence of life! \nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَيْكَ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYKA \nPeace be upon you. May Allah send blessings to you \nوَ عَلٰی آلِ بَيْتِكَ الطَّيَّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ \nWA A’LAA AALE BAYTEKAT TAYYABEENAT TAAHEREENA \nand upon your Household, the pure and immaculate.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ عَجَّلَ اللهُ لَكَ مَا وَعَدَكَ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA A’JJALAL LAAHO LAKA MAA WA-A’DAKA \nPeace be upon you. May Allah hasten that which He has promised you;\nمِنَ النَّصْرِ وَ ظُهُوْرِ الْاَمْرِ \nMENAN NASRE WA ZOHOORIL AMRE \nnamely, victory and prevalence of your authority.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ يَا مَوْلاَیَ \nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA MAWLAAYA \nPeace be upon you, O my master.\nاَنَا مَوْلَاكَ \nANAA MAWLAAKA \nI am a servant of you \nعَارِفٌ بِاُولٰيكَ وَ اُخْرٰيكَ \nA’AREFUN BE OOLAAKA WA UKHRAAKA \nand I recognize the first and the last of your affair.\nاَتَقَرَّبُ اِلَی اللهِ تَعَالٰی بِكَ وَ بِآلِ بَيْتِكَ \nATAQARRABO ELAL LAAHE TA-A’ALAA BEKA WA BE-AALE BAYTEKA \nI seek nearness to Allah, the Exalted, through your Household and you\nوَ اَنْتَظِرُ ظُهُوْرَكَ وَ ظُهُوْرَ الْحَقِّ عَلٰی يَدَيْكَ \nWA ANTAZERU ZOHOORAKA WA ZOHOORAL HAQQE A’LAA YADAYKA \nand I am expecting your advent and the prevalence of the truth at your hands.\nوَ اَسْئَلُ اللهَ اَنْ يُصَلِّیَ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ \nWA AS-ALUL LAAHA AN YOSALLEYA A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN \nAnd I beseech Allah to send blessings to Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad,\nوَ اَنْ يَجْعَلَنِیْ مِنَ الْمُنْتَظِرِيْنَ لَكَ \nWA AYN YAJA’LANEE MENAL MUNTAZEREENA LAKA \nand to include me with those who are expecting you,\nوَ التَّابِعِيْنَ وَ النَّاصِرِيْنَ لَكَ عَلٰی اَعْدَآئِكَ \nWAT TAABE-E’ENA WAN NAASEREENA LAKA A’LAA AA’-DAAAEKA \nthose who follow you and support you against your enemies,\nوَ الْمُسْتَشْهَدِيْنَ بَيْنَ يَدَيْكَ \nWAL MUSTASH-HADEENA BAYNA YADAYKA \nand those who will be martyred in front of you \nفِیْ جُمْلَةِ اَوْلِيَآئِكَ يَا مَوْلاَیَ يَا صَاحِبَ الزَّمَانِ \nFEE JUMLATE AWLEYAAA-EKA YAA MAWLAAYA YAASAAHEBAZ ZAMAANE \nin the group of your loyalists. O my master, O Patron of the Age!\nصَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْكَ وَ عَلٰی آلِ بَيْتِكَ \nSALAWAATUL LAAHE ALAYKA WA A’LAA AALE BAYTEKA \nMay Allah’s blessings be upon you and upon your Household.\nهٰذَا يَوْمُ الْجُمُعَةِ وَهُوَ يَوْمُكَ الْمُتَوَقَّعُ فِيْهِ ظُهُوْرُكَ \nHAAZAA YAWMUL JOMO-A’TE WA HOWA YAWMOKAL MOTAWAQQAO’ FEEHE ZOHOOROKA \nToday is Friday, which is your day on which your advent is expected\nوَ الْفَرَجُ فِيْهِ لِلْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ عَلٰی يَدَيْكَ \nWAL FARAJO FEEHE LIL MOMENEENA A’LAA YADAYKA \nto bring about relief to the believers at your hands,\nوَ قَتْلُ الْكَافِرِيْنَ بِسَيْفِكَ \nWA QATLUL KAAFEREENA BE-SAYFEKA \nand killing of the disbelievers with your sword.\nوَ اَنَا يَا مَوْلاَیَ فِيْهِ ضَيْفُكَ وَجَارُكَ \nWA ANAA YAA MAWLAALYA FEEHE ZAYFOKA WA JAAROKA \nOn this day, O my master, I am your guest and in your vicinity\nوَ اَنْتَ يَا مَوْلاَیَ كَرِيْمٌ مِنْ اَوْلاَدِ الْكِرَامِ \nWA ANTA YAA MAWLAAYA KAREEMUN MIN AWLAADIL KERAAME \nand you, my master, are generous and the descendant of the generous people,\nوَ مَاْمُوْرٌ بِالضِّيَافَةِ وَ الْاِجَارَةِ \nWA MAAMOORUN BIZ-ZEYAAFATE WAL EJAARATE \nand you are commanded to receive your guests and neighbors hospitably; \nفَاَضِفْنِیْ وَ اَجِرْنِیْ \nFA-AZIFNEE WA AJIRNEE \nso, receive me as your guest and neighbor.\nصَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيكَ وَ عَلٰی اَهْلِ بَيْتِكَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ.\nSALAWAATUL LAAHE A’LAYKA WA A’LAA AHLE BAYTEKAT TAAHEREENA.\nMay Allah’s blessings be upon you and upon your Household, the immaculate.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    ", 
    "title": "Ziyarah of Imam al Mahdi (a.t.f.s.) on Friday"
}